cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.AI 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with speech recognition evaluation and error analysis in speech translation. It may also belong to cs.SD (Sound) and cs.SI (Signal Processing) as it involves processing of audio signals. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it proposes a new metric for speech recognition evaluation that incorporates phonetic information, which could be useful in machine learning and AI applications.
